						               													<description>Monster Clashhh! is a fast and fun ROLL &amp;amp; FIGHT game. You have to be first friends with all 5 monsters! When you be a friends with monsters, attack another player! Also you have to keeping the most life points at the same time. Risk management, tactical choices and luck are the keys which will lead you to the victory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gameplay&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1. Every player receives one summoner&amp;rsquo;s sheet.&amp;#10;2. Players play clockwise.&amp;#10;3. First player rolls the four dice, trying to get a combo allowing you to fill the spaces of Monster or the spaces of Special Ability. You can roll 3 times the dices (choosing the one(s) you wanna roll again).&amp;#10;4. When you decide to stop (usually after the 3rd roll), trigger the effect of your final combos according to the rules.&amp;#10;5. When you finish, the player at your left can play his turn (by rolling his dice and completing his summoner&amp;rsquo;s sheet).&amp;#10;6. The game is over when a player succeeds in summoning the five different monsters while having the most HP or if all of his opponents lose all of their HP.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
